strings:
<voice_0x0100167E><center>We are fighting the mighty Lord of Darkness.
<center>He will not be easily defeated.

<voice_0x0100167F><center>But there will always be a glimmer of hope
<center>as long as we refuse to surrender.
<center>As long as we are not subdued.

<voice_0x01001680><center>Stand up to him!
<center>I know you can do it!
The party's HP and MP are fully restored!
